reviewerName: C. Drake "Java Jane of the Jungle"
reviewText: My brother turned me on to these movies.  They are heartwarming and done well!  Everyone in the family can watch these.  The characters are believable and the stories are not contrived.  There is some graphic violence in a few of these DVDs so it may be upsetting for younger kids, but certainly they could watch them.  These were produced my Michael Landon, Jr.  and he has held to his father's high standards.  Great movies with strong heroines!
summary: These are GREAT movies for the whole family!
